title: House of Saud | Royal Family Members & History | Study.com
snippet: The House of Saud is the ruling family of the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, one of the few remaining absolute monarchies in the world. Because of this, the Saudi royal family is extensively wealthy and powerful, dominating the politics and economy of Saudi Arabia.
